Package tcore.messages

Class MatchSet

java.lang.Object
tcore.messages.MatchSet
public class MatchSet extends Object
A container for matches between a Model and a LHS.
Each MatchSet is associated with a single LHS.
Since:
2017-12-08
Version:
0.5
Author:
Pierre-Olivier Talbot, Sebastien Ehouan
